{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"漸進增強","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Progressive_Enhancement","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>漸進增強</strong>（Progressive enhancement）是強調要在受限情境下提供初等體驗、對所有人提供必要的內容與功能、以及需要時再加上其他可選功能的設計哲學。它更接近於強調無障礙、以及許多腳本技術的網站設計策劃。這個技術很有用，因為它讓網路開發者，在專注開發最強大的網站同時，和某些未知的用戶代理，在訪問網站時發生的問題間達到權衡。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解詳情","title":"了解詳情","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基本知識","title":"基本知識","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>維基百科的 <a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%BC%B8%E9%80%B2%E5%A2%9E%E5%BC%B7\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">漸進增強</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"了解詳情","id":"了解詳情"}],"summary":"漸進增強（Progressive enhancement）是強調要在受限情境下提供初等體驗、對所有人提供必要的內容與功能、以及需要時再加上其他可選功能的設計哲學。它更接近於強調無障礙、以及許多腳本技術的網站設計策劃。這個技術很有用，因為它讓網路開發者，在專注開發最強大的網站同時，和某些未知的用戶代理，在訪問網站時發生的問題間達到權衡。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Progressive Enhancement","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Mejora Progresiva","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Amélioration progressive","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Progressive Enhancement (プログレッシブエンハンスメント)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"점진적 향상","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"渐进增强","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/glossary/progressive_enhancement","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/glossary/progressive_enhancement/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary","title":"術語表"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Progressive_Enhancement","title":"漸進增強"}],"pageTitle":"漸進增強 - 術語表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}